its lean six sigma program training and hiring black belts from within and engaging people in lss teams across the company more than  black belts and green belts have been traveling across the company the lean six sigma teams are delivering greater than a sixtoone return on investment in cost savings for lp domestic subsidiaries greenstone industries inc ketchikan pulp company louisianapacific international inc lpspv inc  lp pinewood spv llc lps corporation lp spv llc foreign subsidiaries of louisianapacific corporation louisianapacific canada pulp co  louisianapacific canada sales ulc  louisianapacific canada holding ltd  louisianapacific canada ltd louisianapacific osb ltd louisianapacific south america sa louisianapacific chile sa louisianapacific del perú saclpbrasil osb industria e comercio sa less than  owned joint ventures abitibilp engineered wood inc abitibilp engineered wood ii inc canforlp osb gp corp canforlp osb limited partnership us greenfiber llc principal competitors georgiapacific group boisecascade corporation jamies hardie weyerhaeuser company tolko on september   lp announced plans to acquire vancouver bc based ainsworth lumber in a stock and cash deal estimated at  billion referencesedit  a b c d e f g h i j k louisianapacific corporation funding universe funding universe retrieved  september    lp engineered wood product housing zone reed business information building group retrieved  september    lp building products guide to apa members apa – the engineered wood association retrieved  september    a b c d e f g louisianapacific corporation encyclopediacom highbeam research inc retrieved  september    lpcorp –  relocation to nashville – accessed   wyatt jim june   titans stadium lp field to be renamed nissan stadium the tennessean retrieved june     lewis rick  november  get reoriented the technology behind sustainable building engineered wood retrieved  september    housing starts fell last month new york times  march  retrieved  september  