rmation act foiafoia reading roomusda service centerselectric gfrgfr electric texttelecom gfrgfr telecom textfield accountantsfield accountants textcivil rights contacts twitter blog gov delivery rss flickr facebook home  about rd back to previous page print about rd welcome to usda rural development we are committed to helping improve the economy and quality of life in rural america through our programs we help rural americans in many ways we offer loans grants and loan guarantees to support economic development and essential services such as housing health care first responder services and equipment and water electric and communications infrastructure we promote economic development by supporting loans to businesses through banks credit unions and communitymanaged lending pools we offer technical assistance and information to help agricultural producers and cooperatives get started and improve the effectiveness of their operations we provide technical assistance to help communities undertake community empowerment programs we help rural residents buy or rent safe affordable housing and make health and safety repairs to their homes usda rural development has a  billion portfolio of loans leadershipusda rural development is headed by anne hazlett who is the assistant to the secretary for rural development   learn more officesusda rural development has a loan portfolio of more than  billion to bring enhanced economic opportunity to the nations rural communities to accomplish its goals it relies on a dedicatedlearn more agenciesusda rural development is divided into three agencies with unique missions to bring prosperity and opportunity to rural areas learn more initiativesusda rural development prioritizes funding toward projects under the following initiatives learn more farm billthe agricultural act of  is important legislation that provides authorization for services and programs that impact every american and millions of people around the world the farm billlearn 